<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Charter<font size="4">ed By </font>The British Schools <font size="4">Founda<font size="4">t<font size="4">ion</font></font></font><br></i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="1"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</font></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px;"></span></font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="margin:0;"><font face="Calibri,sans-serif" size="2"><span style="font-size:11pt;"><font color="#002060" size="3"><span style="font-size:12pt;"><br></span></font></span></font><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3">You can type anything from here onwards.&nbsp; <br><br>When you do type a message please make sure you write inside the confines of the current paragraphs to ensure the email displays correctly when it reaches the recipient.<br><br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">When FOR EXAMPLE YOU CAN TYPE YOUR NEW TEXT IN THE MIDDLE OF THE LAST TWO WORDS OF AN EXISTING PARAGRAPH LIKE THIS recipient.</span><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><br><br>Then you can delete the first and last words. This ensures that the hidden HTML tags are not accidentally deleted.<br><br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">When copying a paragraph you should ensure that you copy the area before and after the paragraph as well as the text for the same reason.</span><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><br></font><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><br></font><span style="font-size: medium; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">You can also create links to documents in your emails. For example <a href="https://eu1.salesforce.com/sfc/p/D0000000DDpn/a/D00000004OcW/HwdgvpPL0wkYbSQ78Dlh1K2C03fWCU.10mhq9W7EMGs=">this link</a> will take you to a conditions and declarations form.</span><br style="font-size: medium; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><br></font><span style="font-size: medium; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Last but not least you can also use merge fields in your emails. Merge fields take information from records within Salesforce and allow us to personalize emails. Notice the merge fields on the "Dear" line above. These are the main ones used but it is possible, with a little help, to create emails which pull other information from parent/student/contact records in SF.</span><br style="font-size: medium; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><br>Thank you for reading.<br><br>Warm Regards,<br><br></font></div></span><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">Administration Team</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;"></span></div>]]></td>
